00:00:08.280 --> 00:00:09.580
BRETT SLATKIN: Hey, my name is
Brett Slatkin, and I'm a

00:00:09.580 --> 00:00:11.040
software engineer
here at Google.

00:00:11.040 --> 00:00:14.480
We're here today to talk about
IndieWebCamp and the

00:00:14.480 --> 00:00:18.380
independent web with Tantek
Celik, who's a technologist,

00:00:18.380 --> 00:00:19.980
writer and teacher.

